# PRE-LAUNCH AUDIT CHECKLIST — Namibia Sports Platform

## Database
- [ ] RLS enabled on all Supabase tables
- [ ] Foreign keys with ON DELETE specified
- [ ] Indexes on FKs and frequent WHERE/ORDER BY columns
- [ ] Migrations reversible
- [ ] Connection pooling configured

## Auth
- [ ] Signup → email confirmation → login works
- [ ] Protected routes redirect unauthenticated users
- [ ] RBAC enforced at tRPC level
- [ ] Logout clears session

## API (tRPC)
- [ ] Every procedure has input validation
- [ ] Every procedure has error handling
- [ ] Federation admin scope enforced
- [ ] No secrets in responses

## Security
- [ ] No secrets in codebase
- [ ] .env.example documents all vars
- [ ] CORS restrictive
- [ ] File upload validation

## Performance
- [ ] List queries paginated
- [ ] No N+1 patterns
- [ ] Bundle size reasonable

## Documentation
- [ ] docs/02_database_schema.md current
- [ ] docs/03_api_and_integrations.md current
- [ ] CHANGELOG.md up to date
- [ ] README has working setup instructions
